---
title: About
layout: base.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: About
  order: 3
---

{% block content %}
    <section class="about-hero section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-hero-content">
                <div class="about-hero-image">
                    {% responsiveImage "/assets/images/photographer.jpg", "Photographer portrait", "(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw", { loading: "eager" } %}
                </div>
                <div class="about-hero-text">
                    <h1 class="about-hero-title">About Me</h1>
                    <p class="about-hero-intro">A passionate photographer dedicated to capturing authentic moments and telling compelling stories through imagery.</p>
                    <p class="about-hero-description">With over a decade of experience behind the lens, I've had the privilege of documenting life's most precious moments – from intimate family gatherings to grand celebrations, from sweeping landscapes to compelling commercial work. Every photograph tells a story, and I'm honored to help tell yours.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-story section section-muted">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-story-content">
                <div class="about-story-text">
                    <h2 class="about-story-title">My Story</h2>
                    <p>Photography found me unexpectedly. What started as a casual interest quickly evolved into an all-consuming passion. I spent countless hours learning the craft, experimenting with different techniques, and developing my unique style.</p>
                    <p>Over the years, I've had the opportunity to work with hundreds of clients, each with their own unique story to tell. This diversity of experience has shaped my approach to photography – one that values authenticity, creativity, and genuine connection.</p>
                    <p>Today, I continue to push boundaries and explore new creative possibilities while staying true to the core principles that have guided my work: capturing authentic moments, telling compelling stories, and creating images that resonate.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-expertise section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Areas of Expertise</h2>

            <div class="expertise-grid">
                <div class="expertise-item card">
                    <div class="expertise-icon">
                        <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                            <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="expertise-title">Portrait Photography</h3>
                    <p class="expertise-description">Professional portraits that capture personality and essence. From individual headshots to family portraits.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="expertise-item card">
                    <div class="expertise-icon">
                        <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                            <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line>
                            <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line>
                            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="expertise-title">Event Photography</h3>
                    <p class="expertise-description">Comprehensive coverage of weddings, corporate events, and special occasions. Every moment documented.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="expertise-item card">
                    <div class="expertise-icon">
                        <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="expertise-title">Commercial Photography</h3>
                    <p class="expertise-description">High-impact imagery for brands, products, and marketing campaigns. Elevate your visual presence.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="expertise-item card">
                    <div class="expertise-icon">
                        <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="expertise-title">Fine Art</h3>
                    <p class="expertise-description">Artistic photography that pushes creative boundaries. Limited edition prints available.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-equipment section section-muted">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="equipment-content">
                <div class="equipment-text">
                    <h2 class="equipment-title">Equipment & Gear</h2>
                    <p class="equipment-description">Professional-grade equipment ensures the highest quality results for every project.</p>

                    <div class="equipment-list">
                        <div class="equipment-category">
                            <h3 class="equipment-category-title">Cameras</h3>
                            <ul class="equipment-items">
                                <li>Sony Alpha 7R V</li>
                                <li>Canon EOS R5</li>
                                <li>Fujifilm GFX 100S</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="equipment-category">
                            <h3 class="equipment-category-title">Lenses</h3>
                            <ul class="equipment-items">
                                <li>Sony 24-70mm f/2.8 GM II</li>
                                <li>Sony 85mm f/1.4 GM</li>
                                <li>Canon RF 15-35mm f/2.8L</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="equipment-category">
                            <h3 class="equipment-category-title">Lighting</h3>
                            <ul class="equipment-items">
                                <li>Profoto B10 Plus</li>
                                <li>Godox AD600Pro</li>
                                <li>Aputure 600d</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="equipment-image">
                    {% responsiveImage "/assets/images/equipment.jpg", "Photography equipment", "(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw" %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-cta section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2 class="cta-title">Let's Work Together</h2>
                <p class="cta-description">Whether you have a specific project in mind or just want to explore possibilities, I'd love to hear from you.</p>
                <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
